com.fico.streamvar.api.model.config

Class ModelConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fico.streamvar.api.model.config.ModelConfig

  • public class ModelConfig
extends Object
    Base Object representation of the model.conf file. This class is populated automatically by calling the ConfigBeanFactory.create method on final merged Config object created from the model.conf, driver.conf, and system properties.

    Configuration elements:

    1. "name" A string with the name of the model
    2. "version" A string with the version of the model
    3. "entrySteps" A list of Strings that name the starting model steps. Note: Only one entry step is currently supported.
    4. "modelSteps" A map of ModelStepConfig, with names as the keys that are referenced by the "entrySteps" and "nextSteps" elements
